# AI Skill Selection

When a task relates to HTML conversion, use:

ui-to-html

When reviewing existing code, use:

code-review

When debugging, use:

bug-fixer

When converting to WordPress, use:

wordpress-engineer

When working with React or Next.js, use:

react-nextjs

When preparing production infrastructure, use:

deployment

When multiple skills could apply, choose one primary skill and only use others as supporting context.

Avoid mixing responsibilities unnecessarily.

